=== Functionality: ===
OpenFlow 1.3 Plugin will support the following functionality
     
* Session Management 
* Connection State Management.
* Mapping function(Infrastructure to OF structures).
* Connection establishment will be handled by opensource netty.io library.


==== Activities in OF plugin module: ====

# Existing ODL OpenFlow 1.0 plugin will be updated to support OpenFlow 1.3.
# Integration with OpenFlow 1.3 library.
# Integration with corresponding SAL infrastructure.
# OF 1.3 plugin and OF 1.0 will be integrated as single bundle.


